                  <persName id="t17840915-76-person892">
                  ANN
                   WILSON
               <interp inst="t17840915-76-person892" type="surname" value="WILSON"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840915-76-person892" type="given" value="ANN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840915-76-person892" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I lost the things mentioned in the indictment, I saw them before dinner, there was no light in the house; the prisoner was <rs id="t17840915-76-viclabel380" type="occupation">employed to clean knives</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840915-76-victim891 t17840915-76-viclabel380"></join>; I found the things last Thursday, at Mr. Harding's, in the Minories; the prisoner went past my door, and my mother took him and stopped him; he confessed what he had done with them, I had not seen them from the time they were lost till then; he said he had suffered the law for them, he had been imprisoned, he was stopped with them: Mr. Harding stopped him, and advertized them.</p>
               <p>(The spoon and table cloth produced.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17840915-76-person893">
                  THOMAS
                   HARDING
               <interp inst="t17840915-76-person893" type="surname" value="HARDING"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840915-76-person893" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840915-76-person893" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am a goldsmith, I have a spoon broke in two; the prisoner at the bar brought me this spoon and table cloth, and said he found them coming from Hampstead, as he was mushrooming on Primrose-hill; the spoon was wrapped in the table cloth, I stopped him and sent him to prison.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I have nothing to say.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17840915-76-verdict381" type="verdictDescription">
